io.github.mywarp.mywarp.bukkit

Class DynmapMarker

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.mywarp.mywarp.bukkit.DynmapMarker

  • public class DynmapMarker
extends java.lang.Object
    Displays markers for warps using dynmap.

    Warps are only displayed if they match a filter (Predicate.test(Object)) returns true) given when an instance is created.

    In addition to using the provided methods to manually add or remove warps, instances can be registered at an EventBus that raises WarpEvents to automatically add, update or delete warps when the appropriate events are raised.
